{
  "stem": "21310.5",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I-- to lose them, I would jump on a German trolley cart, or I approach a German and ask some stupid question, some direction, so whoever followed me, you know, would throw-- be thrown off track.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Anyway, that one day, I-- I had to make the train.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I knew my parents would be terribly worried if I didn't get there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the curfew was coming.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So-- and I knew the Germans could only go-- always go.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And so there were these two officers who kind of looked at me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They were more middle-aged-- you know, for me, they were middle-aged, around 30.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And, so I dropped the book.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You know, not a [LAUGHS] handkerchief.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But the book.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And one of them picked it up and saw it was a German book.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So he started to talk to me and I spoke with them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And then the train got there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And no Poles could get in the train, only the Germans.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I held back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And he said, [GERMAN]-- come on, come on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I said, no, I'm not German.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I can't go in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Oh, you know, stupid, and you come as our guest.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "So I-- I went.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "So that's how I made the acquaintance with these two guys.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Well, one was nicer than the other.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "But you know, they ask me about how come I'm Polish if I speak German, why I'm not at [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "So I came back with this my story about my German mother.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And anyway-- but I didn't tell them where I-- where I worked or where I lived, you know.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Once we got there, I said goodbye.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And-- but this one guy, [SIGHS] his name was Ostrus, he found-- he took the train quite frequently.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And he saw me at the railroad station.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
